## Полный поток message/stream

### 1. Client → API

```python
POST /agents/example_react
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "message/stream",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-123",
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{"kind": "text", "text": "Hello"}],
      "contextId": "ctx-456"
    }
  }
}
```

### 2. A2AChannel.on_message_stream()

```python
# Создаём subscriber
subscriber = EventSubscriber(redis_client)

# Запускаем worker
await process_agent_task.kiq(
    agent_id=agent_id,
    task_id=task_id,
    context_id=context_id,
    content="Hello",
    ...
)

# Стримим события клиенту
async for event in subscriber.subscribe(task_id):
    yield event
```

### 3. Worker: BaseChannel.process_task()

```python
# Создаём emitter
emitter = Emitter(redis_client, state)

# Загружаем agent
agent = await agent_factory.get_agent(agent_id)

# Выполняем
try:
    state = await agent.run(state)
    await emitter.emit_complete(state.response)
except AgentInterrupt as e:
    await emitter.emit_interrupt(e.question)
except Exception as e:
    await emitter.emit_error(str(e))
```

### 4. ReactNodeRunner.run()

```python
# LLM stream
async for event in llm.stream(messages, tools):
    if event.type == "text":
        await emitter.emit_text(event.text)
    elif event.type == "tool_call":
        await emitter.emit_tool_call(
            tool_name=event.tool_name,
            tool_args=event.tool_args,
            tool_call_id=event.tool_call_id
        )
```

### 5. Client получает события

```
event: task-status-update
data: {"kind":"task-status-update","taskId":"...","status":{"state":"working"}}

event: task-artifact-update
data: {"kind":"task-artifact-update","artifact":{"parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Hello"}]}}

event: task-artifact-update
data: {"kind":"task-artifact-update","artifact":{"parts":[{"kind":"text","text":" world"}]}}

event: task-status-update
data: {"kind":"task-status-update","status":{"state":"completed"}}
```

